<p>Ink spots decorating white uniform shirts and some nimble fingers, smeared in blue, drawing caricatures on notebook pages and mindlessly playing tic tac toe...</p>
<p>Yes, school days bring back blue. Blue ink, blue skirt, blue jacket, blue sweater, blue tie, blue house,  blue sky, blue water and beautiful indigo blue saris of my favourite teacher, Mrs. Banerjee. Oh and how can I forget what she lovingly called the blue bugs in my pen.</p>
